1] What is Volatile , How it resolves visibilty problem?

 ⚙ CPU cache structure :

    - Cpu with two core
    - each core has local cache & one common shared cache
    - Visibility Problem :
        - If one thread modify the flag value it will  refelects only in local cache
        - when you used volatile keyword it flush  the local cache changes to shared cache and refresh the other
          core cache flag value where other threads are running
    - EX : volatile boolean flag=false;


